data.description: Looking for a cabin in The White Mountains, look no further here it is!  Located on an acre of land, this wonderfully warm and cozy cabin is the perfect place to unwind and enjoy cool summer temps!  Great access, circle drive, plenty of room for RV guests, fenced and room to build a custom garage or shop.  The home is everything cabin with a fireplace, tongue and groove ceilings, open concept, wood floors, and a great loft area. Home would be a great full-time residence or part-time with an AirBNB opportunity too! Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of The White Mountains in Arizona.
